Recommends: caddy
Description: Web-based solar radio spectrometer suite for a station
 e-Callisto NG runs on a Debian/Raspberry Pi OS station and controls one or
 more Callisto receivers, fully operated from a web browser: install wizard,
 live waterfall, scheduling, data browsing, uploads, and health monitoring.
